          <p>
            When you purchase a Pro or Agency license, you receive:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Pro License:</strong> Valid for one (1) WordPress installation</li>
            <li><strong>Agency License:</strong> Valid for unlimited WordPress installations</li>
            <li>One (1) year of plugin updates delivered via our update server</li>
            <li>One (1) year of priority email support</li>
            <li>Access to all Pro features for the licensed site(s)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            After your license term expires, the plugin continues to function, but you will no longer
            receive updates or support unless you renew your license.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            <strong>License Scope:</strong> Licenses are non-transferable and may not be resold, shared,
