          <p>
            We offer a <strong>14-day money-back guarantee</strong> on all new Pro and Agency purchases.
            If our plugin doesn't work for your store, contact us within 14 days of purchase for a full refund.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            To request a refund:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>Email us at support@wooplugin.pro within 14 days of purchase</li>
            <li>Include your order number and reason for the refund</li>
            <li>Deactivate and remove the plugin from your site(s)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Refunds are processed within 5-10 business days. We reserve the right to deny refund requests
            from customers with a pattern of repeated purchases and refunds.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            <strong>Renewal refunds:</strong> Refunds for subscription renewals must be requested within 7 days
            of the renewal charge.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Subscription and Renewal</h2>
          <p>
            Pro and Agency licenses are subscription-based and renew automatically at the end of each
            license term unless canceled.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>You will receive a reminder email before your subscription renews</li>
            <li>You may cancel auto-renewal at any time from your account</li>
            <li>Canceled subscriptions remain active until the end of the current billing period</li>
            <li>After cancellation, you retain access to the plugin but lose update and support access</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            <strong>Pricing changes:</strong> If you cancel and later wish to renew, you will be charged
            the current pricing at that time. Previous promotional or grandfathered rates cannot be restored.
